            <li><span class="font-medium text-[#32869f]">Usage Data:</span> Information on how you access and use our services.</li>
            <li><span class="font-medium text-[#32869f]">Cookies Data:</span> Small files stored on your device to enhance your browsing experience.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-[#32869f]">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#236c82] mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We use the collected data for various purposes:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>To provide and maintain our service</li>
            <li>To notify you about changes to our service</li>
            <li>To provide customer support</li>
            <li>To gather analysis or valuable information to improve our service</li>
            <li>To monitor the usage of our service</li>
            <li>To detect, prevent and address technical issues</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-[#32869f]">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#236c82] mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">3. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            The security of your data is important to us. We strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your personal information, but we cannot guarantee its absolute security.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-[#e7f5f9] p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#32869f] mb-2">Our Security Measures Include:</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-gray-700">
              <li>Encryption of transmitted data</li>
              <li>Regular security assessments</li>
              <li>Secure data storage systems</li>
              <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-[#32869f]">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#236c82] mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">4. Your Data Protection Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal information:
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#32869f] mb-2">Right to Access</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">You have the right to request copies of your personal data.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#32869f] mb-2">Right to Rectification</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">You have the right to request that we correct any information you believe is inaccurate.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#32869f] mb-2">Right to Erasure</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">You have the right to request that we erase your personal data, under certain conditions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#32869f] mb-2">Right to Restrict Processing</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">You have the right to request that we restrict the processing of your personal data, under certain conditions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-[#32869f]">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#236c82] mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">5. Cookie Policy</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We use cookies to improve your browsing experience, analyze site traffic, and personalize content. By continuing to use our site, you consent to our use of cookies.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-[#e7f5f9] rounded-full text-[#32869f] text-sm font-medium">Essential Cookies</div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-[#e7f5f9] rounded-full text-[#32869f] text-sm font-medium">Functionality Cookies</div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-[#e7f5f9] rounded-full text-[#32869f] text-sm font-medium">Analytics Cookies</div>
            <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-[#e7f5f9] rounded-full text-[#32869f] text-sm font-medium">Marketing Cookies</div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-[#32869f]">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#236c82] mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-[#32869f] bg-opacity-10 p-4 rounded-lg inline-block">
            <p class="text-[#236c82] font-medium">Last Updated: March 18, 2025</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 md:p-8 border-l-4 border-[#32869f]">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#236c82] mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">7. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="mailto:sales@lovosis.com" class="flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 bg-[#32869f] hover:bg-[#236c82] text-white rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 justify-center">
